description: Lists available versions of Grafana. These are available when calling CreateWorkspace. Optionally, include a workspace to list the versions to which it can be upgraded.

nested_items.name: grafanaVersions
nested_items.description: The Grafana versions available to create. If a workspace ID is included in the request, the Grafana versions to which this workspace can be upgraded.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use in a subsequent ListVersions operation to return the next set of results.
